I am all about lip combos and very rarely do I put on just one lip product.💁🏻‍♀️
If you dislike the feel of lipstick on your lips, applying a lip balm with a lip liner works amazingly! 
Tip: Use a smudge proof liner, blend it before it sets. Wait a little, then apply your favourite lip balm. Play with colour. A red tinted lip balm looks even better with a brown lip liner) 
#lipcombotutorial #lipcombo
